<div><head>卷一</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.2">《角賦》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.3">夫角，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.4">以類推之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.5">蓋黃帝會群臣于太山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.6">作清角之音。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.7">似兩鳳之雙鳴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.8">若二龍之齊吟；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.9">如丹虵之翹首，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-1a.10">似雄虵之帶矢。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.2">○《御覽》三百三十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.3">《夫沒歸宗未嫁而亡為服議》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.4">婦人夫沒無子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.5">有歸宗更出之義。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.6">今姑愍彼無嗣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.7">令還其黨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.8">欲令更出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.9">則衛莊姜遣陳媯之比也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.10">于兄弟之家者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.11">兄弟宜服周。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.12">受姑命而歸宗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.13">夫之餘親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-2a.14">不應有服。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2b1627_CHANT_001-3a.2">○《通典》九十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
